53
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,640
If...

54
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:14,800
it had been your father’s fault...

55
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:15,640
If...

56
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:17,080
No ifs.

57
