669
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:30,080
- Do you know... - I know.

670
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:32,080
I know.

671
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:35,000
I shouldn’t have lied

672
00:29:35,640 --> 00:29:36,680
