00:31:01,480 --> 00:31:05,830
♪ Life becomes brighter and warmer ♪

712
00:31:05,830 --> 00:31:09,860
♪ Love will last forever and ever ♪

713
00:31:10,370 --> 00:31:13,750
♪ And ever ♪

714
00:31:29,840 --> 00:31:30,800
That wasn’t me.

